::CyberShark::

    "Hell Beast? I've heard that name before, and the name doesn't taste 
right." CyberShark said. Somehow he knew that Hell Beast was an ememy, and 
that he was a treat to his way of life, he must be destroyed. "Who were your 
other comrades? Magmatron might be able to find what happened to them, he has 
very advanced scanners.
    "Magmatron, could you do a planet wide search for the signals of- who are 
they again?" CyberShark asked.
